{
  "stem": "24409.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I tried to make it clear that the illegal immigration is not really illegal.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] As the percentage of retained certificates is figured from the worldwide immigration number, the number of those delayed certificates is most of the time substantial.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Jews of countries with a large Jewish population are making extensive use of this legal possibility to obtain one certificate.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that's legalizing their status after having first entered Palestine without official certification.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Germany has so far made no use of this possibility, while other countries are making extensive use of it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This was not really true.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] We possess-- we have organized such immigration, which we call visa-less or free immigration, for some time and have recently landed just two ships, with-- and I give the number of the ships.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But this is nothing compared to what we can do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We can in a short time, bring at least 5,000 Jews from Vienna to Palestine without any problems for the Jews or for the German government.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And all we need for this is that we are not-- do not find any impediments by the Germans through this.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This and this in more detail is the content of the memorandum, where essentially I said what I said now.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is the Eichmann Memorandum.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I dictated this memorandum, plus to achieve this, we need in one way the cooperation of the Reichsschatzministerium of the Treasury, of you.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said of you, the Reichsschatzministerium.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We need the permission to transform some local currency into foreign currency.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the Greeks, with whom we are dealing, won't-- do not accept German marks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They want pounds or dollars.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is what I am here for.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I told-- well--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only for the currency.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is the important thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
